        <p><a href="ch67s07.html#MonstersH-I91">Nessian warhounds</a> are coalblack mastiffs the size of draft <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horses</a>, often fitted with shirts of <a href="ch75.html#EpicMonsters(A-E)57">infernal</a> chainmail.</p>
        <p><a href="ch67s07.html#MonstersH-I91">Nessian warhounds</a> resemble <a href="ch67s07.html#MonstersH-I86">hell hounds</a>, except as otherwise noted.</p>
